    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable and attractive choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a lovely shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, shifts smoothly, and has a documented service history, ensuring it is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
