    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a project with potential? This car is a diamond in the rough, ready for a dedicated owner to give it the TLC it needs! While it has seen better days and requires some significant mechanical or cosmetic attention, it's an affordable entry point for someone handy or looking for a parts vehicle. Grab this budget-friendly opportunity today!",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention to be roadworthy. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches, deep scratches, and several large dents, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery and a persistent musty odor. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and there are clear signs of fluid leaks that need immediate repair. This is strictly an 'as-is' sale, ideal for a mechanic or someone looking for a major restoration project or a source for parts.",
      "price": 8500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This specimen is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and garage-kept throughout its life. Every surface, from the flawless paintwork to the pristine interior, reflects a level of care that is rarely seen. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade vehicle that drives as impeccably as it looks. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than the absolute best, this car stands in a class of its own.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I've babied this beauty since day one, and honestly, she looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. From the deep, mirror-like finish to the interior that still feels brand new, she\u2019s been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and only brought out for those perfect sunny drives. There might be a microscopic speck here or there from the road, but you\u2019d need a microscope to find them! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and is ready for the next enthusiast to enjoy, this is it. Come on over, let's chat cars, and see why I'm so in love with this one!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a masterclass in atmospheric induction. Featuring the legendary S65 V8 with its 8,400 RPM redline, this example has been meticulously curated for the discerning pilot. The rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014the Achilles' heel of this chassis\u2014have been professionally addressed with VAC coated bearings and uprated gears. The suspension geometry is surgical, benefiting from refreshed bushings and a precision-aligned subframe. Every shift from the 7-speed DCT is crisp, thanks to a GTS-spec software flash that sharpens engagement. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing a mirror-like finish that suggests a life spent under a breathable car cover in a climate-controlled environment. This isn't just a car; it's a high-revving symphony tuned to perfection.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Garage kept. First person with cash takes it. Don't wait.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a living legacy. This Midnight Sapphire grand tourer isn't just a car; it\u2019s a portal to an era where the road was a destination and style was non-negotiable. Every curve of its hand-polished silhouette captures the light like a gemstone, while the interior welcomes you with the heady, rich aroma of premium hand-stitched leather and polished walnut. To turn the key is to awaken a mechanical symphony\u2014a smooth, effortless surge of power that feels less like an engine and more like a heartbeat. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved masterpiece that commands the gaze of every passerby and turns every evening commute into a cinematic escape.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This specimen remains in pristine showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained with uncompromising attention to detail. From its flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, every aspect of this car offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents an unparalleled opportunity to acquire a top-tier asset that has been preserved to the highest possible standards.",
      "price": 47800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    }
